---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Curriculum Vitae"
  description="生物信息学工程师 - 专注于微生物组学与 AI for Science"
  pubDate={new Date('2026-03-13')}
>
  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>👤 个人简介</h2>
    <p>
      生物信息学工程师，专注于<strong>微生物组学（Microbiome Informatics）</strong>数据分析与工具开发。
      热衷于将 AI 技术应用于科学研究，探索<strong>AI for Science</strong>的无限可能。
      开源爱好者，积极参与并维护多个生物信息学相关开源项目。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>🔗 链接</h2>
    <ul class="cv-links">
      <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/alienzj" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@alienzj</a></li>
      <li><strong>OhMeta 组织:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/ohmeta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/ohmeta</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>💼 专业领域</h2>
    <ul class="cv-skills">
      <li>
        <strong>微生物组学分析</strong>
        <span>16S/ITS 扩增子分析、宏基因组组装、物种注释、功能预测</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>生物信息流程开发</strong>
        <span>Nextflow/Snakemake 流程构建、Docker/Singularity 容器化</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>编程语言</strong>
        <span>Python、R、Bash、JavaScript/TypeScript</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>AI for Science</strong>
        <span>机器学习在组学数据中的应用、AI Agent 开发</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>🛠️ 技术栈</h2>
    <div class="cv-tech">
      <div class="tech-category">
        <h4>生物信息工具</h4>
        <p>QIIME2, DADA2, MetaPhlAn, HUMAnN, MEGAHIT, SPAdes, CheckM</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-category">
        <h4>数据分析</h4>
        <p>pandas, scikit-learn, seaborn, ggplot2, Bioconductor</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-category">
        <h4>AI/ML</h4>
        <p>PyTorch, Transformers, LangChain, LLM Agent 框架</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-category">
        <h4>DevOps & HomeLab</h4>
        <p>Docker, Kubernetes, Proxmox, TrueNAS, Ansible, GitOps</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>🏠 兴趣与爱好</h2>
    <ul class="cv-interests">
      <li>
        <strong>🚀 AI Agent</strong>
        <span>探索自主智能体在科研工作流中的应用</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>🖥️ Self-hosted HomeLab</strong>
        <span>搭建家庭实验室，运行各类自托管服务</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>🚴 Biocycle</strong>
        <span>骑行爱好者，享受户外运动的乐趣</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>🏀 篮球</strong>
        <span>保持运动，健康生活</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>🎮 视频游戏</strong>
        <span>独立游戏爱好者，享受沉浸式体验</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cv-section">
    <h2>📦 开源项目</h2>
    <p>
      在 <a href="https://github.com/ohmeta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OhMeta</a> 
      组织下开发和维护多个生物信息学工具与数据分析流程。
      欢迎访问我的 GitHub 了解更多项目详情。
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .cv-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cv-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .cv-section h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .cv-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .cv-links li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .cv-links a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .cv-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .cv-skills {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .cv-skills li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  
  .cv-skills strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .cv-skills span {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  .cv-tech {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .tech-category {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  .tech-category p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .cv-interests {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .cv-interests li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  
  .cv-interests strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .cv-interests span {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>